description:
This solicitation is for the purchase of the renewal for support and maintenance of an EMC unit and related technical specifications.

Bidders can register in the SSC P2P portal in order to:
a. view and access solicitations from SSC;
b. submit a response to a solicitation;
c. receive updates and amendments regarding solicitations;
d. be awarded contracts and receive contract amendments; and
e. submit invoices and receive payment status updates.

To register, please go to https://supplier-fournisseur-sspc.ssc-spcken, clickcatLogin,  and click Register Now. SSC EMC Support Renewal for DND - Amendment 000
